---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="About Us | FirstLayer Digital">
	<main class="max-w-4xl mx-auto mt-16 px-4">
		
		<div class="text-center mb-16">
			<h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-4">Engineering the Future of the Web</h1>
			<p class="text-xl text-slate-600 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
				We don't just build websites. We build digital assets that are fast, secure, and designed to grow with your business.
			</p>
		</div>

		<div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center mb-20">
			<div>
				<h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-4">The Engineer's Advantage</h2>
				<p class="text-slate-600 mb-4 leading-relaxed">
					Most agencies rely on drag-and-drop website builders that create bloated, slow code. At FirstLayer Digital, we take a <strong>Computer Science approach</strong> to web development.
				</p>
				<p class="text-slate-600 mb-4 leading-relaxed">
					We write semantic, compiled code using modern frameworks like Astro and React. This isn't just about code purity—it's about business results.
				</p>
				<p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed font-medium">
					Our hand-coded sites load up to 40% faster than WordPress, which directly improves your Google ranking and keeps customers on your page.
				</p>
			</div>
			
			<div class="bg-slate-50 p-8 rounded-xl border border-slate-200">
				<h3 class="font-bold text-slate-900 mb-4">Our Tech Stack</h3>
				<ul class="space-y-4 text-slate-600">
					<li class="flex items-start">
						<span class="text-blue-500 mr-2 mt-1">✓</span> 
						<span>
							<strong>Astro Architecture:</strong> Sends zero JavaScript to the client by default for lightning-fast speeds.
						</span>
					</li>
					<li class="flex items-start">
						<span class="text-blue-500 mr-2 mt-1">✓</span> 
						<span>
							<strong>Global Edge CDN:</strong> Your site is replicated on servers worldwide so it loads instantly for everyone.
						</span>
					</li>
					<li class="flex items-start">
						<span class="text-blue-500 mr-2 mt-1">✓</span> 
						<span>
							<strong>Perfect SEO Score:</strong> Structure that search engines love, built right into the core.
						</span>
					</li>
				</ul>
			</div>
		</div>

		<div class="text-center